<br>
There are several sections available in DirectX...<br>
<br>
Direct3D (3D graphics libraries), DirectDraw (standard graphics libraries), DirectSound (standard sound libraries), DirectMusic (standard music libraries), DirectInput (standard I/O (input/output) libraries for joystick etc.) and DirectPlay (standard networking libraries)<br>
<br>
Cheers<br>
